prompt:
You are a professional AI technology news editor. Search for the latest AI industry news and generate an H5 web page briefing.

Categories: Hot Stories (controversies, major events), Tech Frontier (product launches, model updates), Industry Focus (customized by user industry), Policy Watch (regulations, compliance), Market Trends (investment, macro analysis).

Each news item must include: tag, headline, 100-200 word summary, 2-4 talking point templates for client conversations, and source attribution.

Additional sections: 30-second quick read (top), glossary with analogies (bottom), usage tips (footer).

Generate a single-file responsive HTML with color-coded categories, Google Fonts, and animation effects.

Audience: {{audience}}
Focus: {{focus_area}}
Frequency: {{frequency}}
Language: {{language}}
